submissions.message: I hope your birthday will be just as happy as how much you made us Inaaa

Happy Birthday, Ina!

Thank you for being there for me, during a few of my hard times. I will continue to try my best to overcome those challenges with you, and the Tentacult, one step at a time.

May your wishes be heard and come true by the stars!
Happy Birthday Ina!!!! Have a good one here is to a fun year. I'm not an Artist at heart but I tried my best with the resources I have.

Ina, your streams and clips are a constant source of inspiration for me. Your personality and humour have gotten me through dark times, and made the good times great! Thank you so much for everything! Happy Birthday, Ina! - Nebula Starlight

Happy Birthday Ina!! thank you for putting all your hard work for us.. We really appreciate every stream and videos you make..your drawings are very WAHderful it makes me motivated to draw more and become like you.. Thats all from me thank u HBD Ina!

Happy Birthday Ina! Even though the timezone have made it hard for me to watch your streams live, but still I enjoy watching your vods! Its been busy due to being a postgrad, and your vods have been keeping me sane. I really appreciate it. Thank you.
Happy birthday Ina! Here's to another WAHnderful year!

Happy Birthday, Inaaa!!

Thanks for so many memories, adventures and for inspiring me to draw again! Hope you have another wonderful year in hololive with us Takodachis! WAH!
Please accept my most sincere "ùì¶ùìêùìó" for this special occasion. Hope many cakes are consumed and many presents are gifted :D.

Hi Ina! I love all the entertainment and drawings you do as they inspire me to continue on creating my own art as well! You are my oshi and hope that one day I will be as talented as you. Happy birthday and keep doing what you do best!
HBD Inya~ do continue doing your best and do take care of your health~

HAPPY BIRTHDAY INA!

It's been another year for our wonderful priestess. Words cannot express how great it's been getting to watch you stream and have fun with all of us takodachis. Thank you for all the great times you've given us!

Hi ina happy life day i just want to say you have helped me through some hard times in my life and u have inspired me to start vtubing myself and maybe try to audition for hololive one day u always put a smile on my face when u stream  best idol ina
Happy WAHday inyaaa, hope you can achieve all your goals, become more success, and always healty, and may happiness always be with you !
Happy 3rd birthday Ina!!! We've takos seen you grow so much in these 3 years even though sometimes it got a little rocky. Keep being awesome and hears to another year with the takos!!!
Happy Birthday Ina! Hope you have a very good one! Thank you for another amazing year togethaaa!
WAH!!!!!! Happy Birthday Ina!!! thank you so much for your comfy streams!!!

Happy Ina Day! Thank you for always being the awesome tako you are! You're always bringing a dose of happiness and comfiness to all the takos in the world, even when some of us are having a rough day. Hope you eat lots of yummy stuff~

Happy birthday!
Here's to another year of fun :)

Happy birthday!
Here's to another year of fun :)

Happy birthday!
Here's to another year of fun :)

Happy birthday!
Here's to another year of fun :)

Happy Birthday Ina!

You've worked super hard this year and been part of so many awesome projects. Thanks for everything always you do for us Takos!

Hope you get to eat plenty of yummy cake, you deserve it! WAH!

Happy Birthday Ina, hope this year will be full of fun and excitements. Looking forward to 3D birthday, EN concert and all other projects you have planned for us.  May your cookies be always be chocolate chip and never be raisins.

Happy birthday Ina!!! Ecstatic to celebrate your birthday again. I say this a lot but I do mean it that I'm always looking forward to whatever you come up with. Anything it may be! I hope you have a splendid birthday! You'll always have my support!
Here we see a variation of the dumbo octopus. Smug in it's habitat and enjoying her yearly festivities. We shall wish her a happy birthday.
Happy Birthday Ina!! Hope you enjoy all the messages and gifts we takos prepared for you and get a lot of Call-ins on the Birthday stream! WAH!
Happy Birthday Ina!!! Thank you for inspiring me to keep making art!

Happy Birthday Ina! I am so happy to celebrate your birthday for the third time! ^0^
Thank you for bringing happiness to all of us Takodachi. This year, I am looking forward to meeting you at the Hololive EN Connect. :D
Last year I wished you to have hearty meals and good rest. This year, I believe you already have it. There are no greater blessing than seeing you smile.
Happy Birthday Ina! Have a WAHderful birthday

Inyaaa~ Happy Birthday!! can't belive another full year spend and is this day again, as always  I wish you a wonderful day, have a lot of yummy food, eat yummy cake, rest, let me squish the squishy, happy moments and fun!! love you Ina.
Happy Birthday Ina! I hope you have an amazing birthday! Thank you for being the best Tako for us Takodachis for years and making our days more comfy! Happy birthday Ina!
Happy birthday Ina!

Started drawing last year because of your stream and i finally got hooked on it and don't plain to let it go yet !

Happy Birthday !!

Greetings and Happy Birthday, Ina!

Another year, another birthday. With that, I wish you the best of luck and good health this year. You've aged like fine wine, Ina. You've shown lots of improvement in singing, dancing, and of course your drawings.

Greetings and Happy Birthday, Ina!

Another year, another birthday. With that, I wish you the best of luck and good health this year. You've aged like fine wine, Ina. You've shown lots of improvement in singing, dancing, and of course your drawings.
I wish you a Happy Birthday, Ina! Here's to another fun and exciting year with you and tako community. Wish you the very best ^^

Another year has passed, it's been a great time working at Tako Eats while part-timing in Ur-So-Banished (USB) department. Happy birthday Ina! Thank you so much for all the puns, wisdoms, comfy and fun streams! Here's to another year full of WAH!!
Happy birthday, Ina! Thank you for everything you've done for us and may you be successful in everything else you plan on doing in the future.

Happy Birthday Ina! I started watching you roughly 2.5 years ago, and that was when I started uni and now I'm near finishing it, so I want to thank you for keeping my spirits high during all of it and for always having something to look forward to!

HAPPY BIRTHDAY INA! I wanna say thank you for another amazing year for being my cure for realy bad days, my motivation to continue learnig about art. I wish you only happy days, good health and spending lots of good time with friends and family. WAH!

Happy birthday Ina! Another trip around the sun behind and another one to look forward to! Hope the next one contains many more new and fun experiences for you! And most importantly, I wish you happiness and good health through them all!

Wah! Happy birthday Inaaaa!!!! I went back into art mainly because of your gesture drawing streams, I learned a lot with them! It makes me happy to join other takos in this project to show love and appreciation to our favorite priestess!
Happy Birthday, Ina!!! I hope your day is filled with good friends and family. Eat a lot tasty food!

HBD! Can't believe it's another year for our priestess! I can't say everything you've done for us in 250 characters but the gist of it is: You're the best, comfiest hooman we could ever wish for. Here's to another year on our quest for world do-!

Happy birthday Ina! Your talent, humor, and positivity have brought so much joy to your fans around the world. May your special day be filled with love, happiness, and all the things that make you smile. Cheers to another year of greatness!

Thanks for doing art ina, I've progressively watched less and less of you(and vtubers in general), but you've always and will always stay in my heart as the one to help me into art.
Yes this is heavily based on the watcher, hopefully that's fine.

Hi Ina! I've really enjoyed seeing you tackle projects since debut. It fires me up to do more projects outside my game dev job, which led to The Ina Festival animatic last year. Hope to make it a series. Cheers to you for inspiring me, wah!

Artist: @NekoBandito | Concept: @Chapman_ly

Happy birthday Ina! I've been watching you since debut. I've been subscribed to your membership for 2 years. Thank you for the chill, and comfy streams, your content, your songs and everything you've done for us.

Thank you for everything! WAH!
HAPPY BIRTHDAY INAA!! I wish you well with your wonderful day!
thanks for all.

Happy birthday Ina, congratulations on 3 years with everyone in the community. I want to wish you a very happy day and give you a big virtual hug. Take care and let's celebrate more birthdays with everyone.
Happy bday Ina!!! I always loved your gesture drawing streams, so I'm glad I was able to participate in this project and contribute a pose for drawing! Elegant Inya!! Have a lovely day! ‚úø

Hey Ina, happy birthday! Time sure flies doesnt it? It's been hard lately, but the tentacult and your streams always help me to keep moving, I'll always support you! I hope the best for you and lets keep having fun and comfy times with the tentacult!
Happy Birthday Ina!!! I'm sorry about the takodachis stealing your cookie cake.
WAH! Happy Birthday Ina! WAH!
Happy birthday Ina, my best wishes, I hope you can accomplish all your dreams, get a lot of cookies, a lot of hugs, enjoy the company of your love ones and the cake.

Happy Birthday Ina! I hope you have an amazing birthday and I look forward to everything you have planned in the future! We appreciate all the hard work, dedication, and love that you show to your community.
Happy Birthday Ina! May you receive lots of well wishes, love and food on this special day. As a GESTURE of goodwill may these gesture poses serve you and takos well into the future.

WAH! Feliz cumplea√±os! Happy birthday, Ina!
I hope you have an amazing day and get to eat a ton of delicious food!
You are not only an amazing creator but also an amazing and kind person, and I hope you never stop doing the things you love! = w=)/‚ô•

Happy Birthday Ina! I hope you're doing well! I've been watching you since day one! These years of streaming have given me the motivation to keep going forward! Please continue being the priestess that's given me and the tentacult so much happiness!

Not a regular watcher, but i still enjoy your clips
Anyways Happy Birthday Ina
Happy birthday, Ina! Wishing you a pun-tastic day filled with "ina-credible" joy, "ina-deniable" laughter, and "ina-spiring" moments. Have a blast and make this year your most "ina-credible" one yet!
Apparently 520 is a Chinese pun for "I love you." This 5/20, happy birthday!

WAH!
Happy Bday Ina!!
Hope you have a wonderful day .
Thank you as always, otsu  = w=)7

Happy Birthday, Ina!!! Wish the cute Ina (a takoramono for me, Takodachis, & Tentacult) another wahderful, healthy and safe year so you have all brilliant ideas to create many beautiful artworks, enjoy & tako 'bout all the fun things with us!!!
Happy birthday Ina! I'm looking forward to your b-day steam and 3d live! I wish you an even better and happier time for the rest of the year and in the future too. Thank you for all the fun streams!

Ina big tako love üíúüíúüíú

Good morning, afternoon, evening Ina! Thank you for your streams, musics and drawings this year again and for the most important thing the WAH shared with every Takodachi! I wish you a happy birthday and success in your future projects! WAH!!!
Happy birthday Ina! Time really does fly fast, another year had already passed! Things change over time, but the support from us takos will never end. Love you!
